  "body": "<!-- ✨ Jerry’s Mod – Light-Friendly Description ✨ -->\n<div style=\"font-family:Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; color:#333; padding:1.5rem; border-radius:12px; max-width:900px; margin:auto;\">\n\n  <!-- Header -->\n  <h2 style=\"text-align:center; font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1rem; color:#2e7d32;\">\n    🟢 The Legend of Jerry\n  </h2>\n\n  <!-- Backstory -->\n  <p style=\"text-align:center; line-height:1.6; max-width:780px; margin:0 auto 1.5rem;\">\n    Deep underground, <strong>CaptainSparklez</strong> was mining in the world of Minecraftia… when suddenly, a curious slime appeared.\n    Not just any slime — it was <strong>Jerry</strong>, the legendary companion!\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"text-align:center; line-height:1.6; max-width:780px; margin:0 auto 1.5rem;\">\n    Jerry offered his trust — and with it, powerful forbidden gear long hidden from Minecraftia.  \n    Sparklez, now armed with Jerry’s tools, was able to conquer his toughest missions.\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"text-align:center; font-style:italic; margin-top:1.5rem;\">\n    Now it's your turn. Reunite with Jerry. Discover the gear. Embrace the legend.\n  </p>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:0; height:1px; background:#ccc; margin:2rem 0;\">\n\n  <!-- Links -->\n  <h2 style=\"text-align:center; font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem; color:#2e7d32;\">🔗 Useful Links</h2>\n  <ul style=\"text-align:center; list-style:none; padding:0; font-weight:500;\">\n    <li><a href=\"http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/mapping-and-modding/minecraft-mods/1291777\" style=\"color:#1e88e5;\">Minecraft Forum (Current)</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/mapping-and-modding/minecraft-mods/1287930\" style=\"color:#1e88e5;\">Minecraft Forum (Old)</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/mod/jerrry-mod/\" style=\"color:#1e88e5;\">Planet Minecraft</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"https://github.com/NicosaurusRex99/Jerry-s-Mod\" style=\"color:#1e88e5;\">GitHub Repo</a></li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <hr style=\"border:0; height:1px; background:#ccc; margin:2rem 0;\">\n\n  <!-- Video -->\n  <h2 style=\"text-align:center; font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem; color:#2e7d32;\">🎥 Showcase Video</h2>\n  <div style=\"position:relative; padding-bottom:56.25%; height:0; overflow:hidden; border-radius:10px; max-width:100%; margin-bottom:1rem;\">\n    <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Dz4F9NrZoA?wmode=transparent\"\n            style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; border:0;\"\n            allowfullscreen></iframe>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center; font-size:0.95rem; margin:0;\">\n    <em>This video is a classic! Recipes remain unchanged — only the gear stats have been updated.</em>\n  </p>\n</div>\n",
